reviews.review_text: I would like to thank you for Minah Lee her excellent job helping me buying and selling real estate transactions. I really  appreciated her for knowledge, honesty, trustworthiness, and no pressure approach. She understands my needs and always assist me with different perspective & good suggestion. I highly recommend Minah as your realtor because she can fulfill your real estate dreams.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for great review!

reviews.review_text: We used Minah to sell our townhouse and purchase our new house. She was knowledgeable, patient and very quick to respond when we had questions and inquiries. She is professional and easy to deal with.  I would recommend her to anyone looking to sell or buy a property.   She did all the market research in the areas we sold and bought in. We will use her again in the future.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for your kind words, Niki. it was such a pleasure to work with you, I wish you a tons of happiness in your new home.

reviews.review_text: We had a great purchasing experience with Minah. She exceeded our expectation from finding correct property to completion in this multi-offering market and listened to our needs very carefully. I would recommend realtor Minah lee if you plan buy / sell property in Vacouver/Fraser area.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you much for taking time to leave wonderful review! I hope you guys enjoy your new place and the beautiful view for a long time!

reviews.review_text: I have used Minah to sell, buy, sell and buy again. Each experience has been excellent. She is always available to answer my questions and does her best to give me good advices.  Minah is patient and friendly.  She also does not pressure to make decisions. Highly recommended. Many thanks to Minah!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for your kind words. It was a pleasure working with you and your family.

reviews.review_text: I received amazing service from Minah. She was very well informed realtor in the area and very quick to my questions and concerns. I definitely recommend her to anyone looking for to buy or sell properties.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for your review and I appreciate you taking the time out to do this!

reviews.review_text: I liked that she was responsible and treated like a family.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for your valuable review. I really appreciate it.

reviews.review_text: I received a lot of help when I purchased a house last year. I was glad that I could trust the friendly person and the way he did everything he could to help me. Next time I buy or sell real estate, I would like to contact Lee Min-ah again.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for trusting and choosing me I will do my best and work faithfully.

reviews.review_text: I recently sold my house through Mina. From the time we decided to sell our house, ~ they made all the preparations and decorated the house beautifully ~ until the last day of showing and receiving an offer, they worked with passion as if it were my own job! ~ They sold the house in one week at the best price beyond our imagination. Thank you, Minah, who is kind, yet has all of her sincerity, trust, and skills. I really appreciate it. Now I have to buy a house ~ Im really looking forward to it.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for taking the time out of your busy schedule and giving us a really valuable review. I think they both took care of the house beautifully and put a lot of effort into the sale together with me. From now on, I will work even harder to prepare for the house I am moving into. thank you

reviews.review_text: Ms. Mina carefully looks after her as if she were choosing her own house. It was nice to be able to see and choose as many houses as I wanted to see comfortably and without any burden. thank you
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the nice review~
